Tassadit Aïssou (amụrụ na Junnu 19, 1989, na Sidi Aïch, Béjaïa) bụ onye Algeria na egwu volleyball na onye egwuregwu Olimpik na anọchite anya Algeria. Ọ bụ onye na egbochi etiti. Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Chouhada Chikhoune na Béjaïa.

Aïssou nọchitere anya Algeria na Asọmpi Volleyball nke ụmụ nwanyị Afrịka na 2007, 2009, 2011, na 2013; 2009 Mediterranean Egwuregwu; 2008 na 2012 Summer Olimpik; 2010 FIVB Asọmpi mba ụwa; 2011 Egwuregwu Afrịka niile; 2011 FIVB Iko Mbaụwa 2011 Egwuregwu Arab;2012 Asọmpi klọb nke Afrịka; na 2013 na 2014 FIVB Volleyball Ukwu ụwa Prix.
